    dc:creator "Barboza, Gloria E.", "Knapp, Sandra", "Saerkinen, Tiina" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A revision of the South American species of the Morelloid clade (Solanum L., Solanaceae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "342" ;
    bibo:journal "PhytoKeys" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-08-29" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "231" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure35>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure36>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure37> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure35>
    dc:description "Figure 35. Solanum chenopodioides A habit B detail of adaxial leaf surface C detail of abaxial leaf surface D opening bud E dissected flower F fruiting branch G detail of infructescence H maturing fruit I fully mature fruit (A-E Fox s. n. F-I Hieronymus s. n.). Illustration by R. Wise. Previously published in Barboza et al. (2013: 242), Saerkinen et al. (2018: 67) and Knapp et al. (2019: 46)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897496" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure36>
    dc:description "Figure 36. Solanum chenopodioides A habit B buds C flowers at full anthesis D fully mature dull black fruits with appressed calyx lobes (A-D Nijmegen acc. # A 14750051). Photos by S. Knapp and G. van der Weerden. Previously published in Saerkinen et al. (2018: 68) and Knapp et al. (2019: 47)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897497" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure37>
    dc:description "Figure 37. Distribution map of Solanum chenopodioides in South America. For distribution elsewhere see Saerkinen et al. (2018: 70) and Knapp et al. (2019: 50)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897498" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

